{"tid":1838788,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"永安取消明日至2月15日期間出發所有中国線旅行團","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:00:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69a06ff3a74d2a0bfdecbc6c1659976440f9f071","tid":1838788,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"永安旅遊表示，因應內地肺炎疫情和部分景區停止接待旅客，取消年初一至2月15日期間出發的所有中國線旅行團。<br />\n<br />\n永安解釋，在審視最新情況後，需要保障顧客和員工的健康，受影響的顧客可選擇轉往其他旅行團、保留團費6個月，或者減除手續費後退回團費。<br />\n<br />\n永安指，已經通知旅遊業議會有關安排，亦會盡快聯絡受影響的團友跟進；公司會密切留意相關地區的最新情況，有需要時作適當的調整安排。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504600-20200124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504600-20200124.htm&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=f184de59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504600-20200124.htm&h=8a820bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504600-20200124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b590013c48f57bd09c6a3ed1fa4835f0cf101414","tid":1838788,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c407238968a25d868985e52d9fe81778fc5eb99f","tid":1838788,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:59:36.000Z","msg":"琴日先好威威如常出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0290c809ea92d50710a9a8e8b0b8adb6e723a1","tid":1838788,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c407238968a25d868985e52d9fe81778fc5eb99f","tid":1838788,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:59:36.000Z","msg":"琴日先好威威如常出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":